{"type": "article", "id": 3744, "title": "迷你型鸡尾酒套装", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-21T08:09:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233238x9A6VEr2PShIpuwM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t漫长的旅途中，除了需要一个靠谱的护颈枕，一本心爱的小说，也许一杯自己亲手调制的鸡尾酒才是最棒的放松方式。日前，来自纽约布鲁克林的 W&amp;P Design 工作室和 Punch 公司就携手带来一款迷你型鸡尾酒套装。整个套装包含有一份原产自委内瑞拉的 Aromatic Bitters 酒、两包蔗糖、一张配方卡、一根搅拌棒以及一片亚麻材质的杯垫，这样你就可以在旅途中轻松调制一杯鸡尾酒啦。整体套装的设计极具复古风情，定价 24 美元，<a href=\"http://carryoncocktailkit.com/?variant=976313539\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052332375adA87bysLHfiMpW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233237bVCvMuUEcp7tKfX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233238yWIpMvbfjDZBU76S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}